snippet.title: Jason Momoa Speaks On Emilia Clarke Being A Better "Mera" Than Amber
snippet.description:
Jason Momoa Speaks On Emilia Clarke Being A Better "Mera" Than Amber
Jason Momoa claims Amber Heard was fired from Aquaman 2 for a purpose. Jason Mamoa has been generating headlines in the entertainment business for a long time. Indeed, with the release of Aquaman earlier this year, he has become the buzz of Hollywood, and he has been cast in a variety of roles in numerous films, causing us to speculate. Due to Aquaman's tremendous success immediately following its release, the next time we see this heartthrob on the big screen will be in 2022.
